{"tid":1494384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［關於罷課］老師入黎唔該!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-21T15:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T02:00:38.000Z","uid":278383,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ad7f2711b45afa73723db603736d231a1a29bc","tid":1494384,"uid":278383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"求下你地咁多位老師<br />\n唔係迫你地表態<br />\n但一份匿名問卷都唔肯填<br />\n話驚抽後算賬<br />\n你擔心比老細鬧<br />\n我明白<br />\n我體諒<br />\n---<br />\n前線嘅中學生<br />\n暪住老豆老母上街<br />\n翻到學校要面對d藍絲<br />\n罷課驚追唔到學業<br />\n罷課驚被老師鬧<br />\n罷課驚被校長抽後算賬<br />\n佢地前線係前面流汗流血<br />\n面對10年嘅刑期都出黎<br />\n---<br />\n我求下你地可唔可出黎<br />\n同班學生一齊<br />\n陪著班學生<br />\n夠多人唔使驚<br />\n---<br />\n同埋如果你係擔心學生學業<br />\n試著去解決問題<br />\n唔好解決提出問題嘅人<br />\n---<br />\n目前方法有<br />\n放學補課<br />\n放學補習<br />\n搵learning material比學生當功課<br />\n---<br />\n今日你大佬係你自己<br />\n唔係教育局份指引<br />\n---<br />\n幫推！<br />\n---<br />\n你甘心比一d比你年輕十年嘅學生<br />\n背負住比你沈重嘅後果咩？"},{"pid":"6a81ce1ce366e7b2f03d4ab105364f2d51f05ea9","tid":1494384,"uid":278383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:32:27.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推文"},{"pid":"54b4bee9aea22267d89f31efee92a75877f1a9bc","tid":1494384,"uid":278383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"求下幫手推<br />\n冇老師嘅力量<br />\n中學生好難罷<br />\n求下你地<br />\n幫下手"},{"pid":"a93ffb4eac7241117c8397932f176b3b33a5f2d2","tid":1494384,"uid":182770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ead7c67ce2017aae7fe5f0e058ae8966dbfa6937","tid":1494384,"uid":278383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"82fa357e7b16024ce283bbcf7226c99155a6ca1a","tid":1494384,"uid":182770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07dc0361f64e69ce825dcd3920b4141a09e032e8","tid":1494384,"uid":116793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019